        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Police and Fire Health Care Protection Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill eliminates the requirement that payments be made directly to providers of accident or health plans or qualified long-term care insurance contracts as a condition of eligibility for the tax exclusion of distributions from tax-exempt retirement plans for such health and long-term care insurance.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
